title: Nvidia earnings: What to expect from the AI darling
text: Nvidia (NVDA) is set to report third quarter earnings for the fiscal 2025 on Wednesday, November 20. Goldman Sachs managing director Toshiya Hari joins Seana Smith and Madison Mills on Catalysts to discuss what to expect from the key artificial intelligence (AI) player.
